{
  "stem": "4693.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he got so cranky with me, and was dissatisfied.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The next day, he's going special courier to the headquarters for Europe for UNRRA to discharge me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the next day, he went to the swimming pool and got a heart attack and died.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I immediately arranged for somebody else to take over provisionally his job, because I was frightened of his girlfriend who was administrative officer.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was an English girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was-- she knew this story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was very much against me, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But anyway, she was kicked out of UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Then the next fellow, this was interesting thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were under-- all our supply and everything was coming under special department of military government.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the head of the department was American colonel, Decker, who came from Texas, very nice guy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was extremely helpful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was always in contact with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, one day, we got the information there is a new director coming, but that he's a mulatto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Beaufort was his name, Lincoln Beaufort.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And when I went to Munich to see Decker, I told him this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he became white, like this sheet of paper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he said to me, Manny, from now on, any contacts between your headquarters and our headquarters by telephone or letter.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I knows that it's wrong, but this is in my blood-- I don't deal with niggers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And he never came close.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was a very nice guy, otherwise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And one day came a major in connection with some building stories-- he was Jewish, an engineer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I was-- he saw me, and I was-- I knew him and I was showing to him to our headquarters.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I open the door of Beaufort's office.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
